{"tid":2326180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅、Dawn穿「整套肉胎緊身衣」　前衛畫面嚇歪網：時尚好難懂！","createTime":"2020-12-15T06:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T08:16:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2ff27054bc774eaa534f454dfac6b948286a8d","tid":2326180,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女星泫雅身材性感、舞蹈實力堅強，許多男生、女生心中追捧的偶像，每每推出歌曲都會大受歡迎，跟男友Dawn（E&rsquo;Dawn）穩定交往4年，兩人性格互補，一個開朗活潑、一個冷靜有耐心，時常透過社群網站放閃，14日大方貼出穿著情侶裝的照片，大膽的打扮引起許多網友討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5334/5334204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5334%2F5334204.jpg&h=431d8249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅、Dawn交往4年，常常大方放閃。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG）<br />\n<br />\n泫雅14日晚間在Instagram更新近況，貼出了一系列與Dawn的合照，只見兩人穿著膚色長袖緊身上衣與同樣花紋的緊身長褲，大方穿著一模一樣的情侶裝放閃，她開心地在貼文底下寫下「新買的保暖衛生衣，好溫暖」，更直呼與男友穿著膚色的新衣，看起來就像狐獴一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5334/5334202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5334%2F5334202.jpg&h=85728bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅曬出和Dawn穿著新衣的閃照。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG）<br />\n<br />\n然而，泫雅與Dawn穿著膚色緊身衣的照片曝光後，也立刻引起許多粉絲討論，紛紛留言「Dawn的表情有亮點，感覺就是泫雅逼迫她穿著拍照，但還是很寵女友地答應，好幸福喔」、「果然只有你們可以駕馭」，但是前衛的造型也嚇壞了不少網友，忍不住直呼「時尚好難懂」、「看起來真的像奶奶在穿的」、「第一次看男生這樣穿，好衝擊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5334/5334203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5334%2F5334203.jpg&h=49d88b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅和Dawn前衛的造型引起許多網友討論。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，泫雅與Dawn穿的這一套服裝，是來自來自法國的潮牌，招牌圖案就是兩人身上的彎月，是許多時尚明星都非常喜愛的品牌，像是BLACKPINK的Jennie就曾在《DDU-DU DDU-DU》MV 中穿過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5199/d5199466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5199%2Fd5199466.jpg&h=3ed225e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cc9f9bbea18e4ebe5fda8d0468e476cfd3463ad","tid":2326180,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前衛到想交配"},{"pid":"4949652fc624db6915e27668d2d4742c98f38b61","tid":2326180,"uid":374400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"件衫真係醜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3438dc46671280a9c7f16a0f80cf7d387a9d7c","tid":2326180,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc9f9bbea18e4ebe5fda8d0468e476cfd3463ad","tid":2326180,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前衛到想交配"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"勁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfdc560a8b4b8d1deb0fab7a8b23e3ce65bff51","tid":2326180,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4949652fc624db6915e27668d2d4742c98f38b61","tid":2326180,"uid":374400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"件衫真係醜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"fashion既野我識條春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae82860237aabba50c47f8e637e201599e28ac40","tid":2326180,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"唔知屌過幾多次"},{"pid":"cf8000a6e7a3c23f891bd79441776971140377ec","tid":2326180,"uid":